content":"### Step 1 — Welcome (Slack)\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Wait Before Step 2 · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,280],"id":"e4741243-f4ec-4a6e-5b0f-7158cef41dab","name":"Note: Step 1 — Welcome (Slack)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag for Slow Nurture\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,880],"id":"35b3a879-7175-52c3-ae23-8cd8a4d4ebc8","name":"Note: Tag for Slow Nurture"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Wait Before Step 2\n\nPauses 3 days — spacing calls to respect rate limits.\n\nNext: Converted Already?","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,520],"id":"a74298eb-2410-0281-c4b0-5951dfb6c566","name":"Note: Wait Before Step 2"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Converted Already?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.status }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Step 2 — Value Nudge (Slack) · ②→ Mark Converted — Stop Drip","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,520],"id":"83a1a972-9de7-97a6-ca53-624ec7b8ae9f","name":"Note: Converted Already?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Step 2 — Value Nudge (Slack)\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Update Drip Status · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,280],"id":"48080fa0-7669-4a60-2c88-6b6f68577842","name":"Note: Step 2 — Value Nudge (Slack)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Mark Converted — Stop Drip\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,880],"id":"843ec6a3-6035-e89a-2f19-16913576f7c3","name":"Note: Mark Converted — Stop Drip"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Update Drip Status\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Cap Batch Volume · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,520],"id":"c6565082-e55d-1bf7-55f6-f5ea3ae9f44a","name":"Note: Update Drip Status"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cap Batch Volume\n\nCaps the stream at 50 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"d251b790-3997-f2ea-4954-d8163225a61f","name":"Note: Cap Batch Volume"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (HubSpot)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"15a52c9e-17ca-eb61-d345-192f19958421","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (HubSpot)\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"de8d697c-7f0c-dbc5-f45f-abb75e2e38cb","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (HubSpot)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"f482b8bb-8744-2524-c674-83384ca003bd","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,1540],"id":"a5129a57-5900-f73f-5494-b468cdf81295","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,1540],"id":"da9359e6-3037-766f-eb34-c3948bfedf9b","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Route demo requests with HubSpot and Slack for your team\n\n**Pattern:** Lead Capture & Routing · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Form\n\n## What it does\nRoute demo requests with HubSpot and Slack for your team. It starts from a hosted form submission.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual enrichment is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nNew Lead Form Submission → Keep Valid Leads → Segment Audience → Step 1 — Welcome (Slack) → Wait Before Step 2 → Converted Already? → Step 2 — Value Nudge (Slack) → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to lead capture & routing without manual effort\n- Anyone automating enrichment in sales\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n- Standardizes the process every time\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: HubSpot private-app token; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"d753a834-d043-00d9-432a-518c63c36e77","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-260],"id":"b286605f-67c5-d81b-3d7e-5319ffe88216","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## ⏱ Rate limiting\n\nWork is batched and spaced with Wait so provider quotas aren't tripped. If you hit 429s, lower the batch size or raise the wait — throughput drops, reliability rises.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-260],"id":"1c532a12-fdcb-63e0-9ad7-ec67450016a1","name":"⏱ Rate limiting"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your enrichment process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-260],"id":"fd5a67cb-b5d7-e84a-d1ef-e4243216b6ab","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"New Lead Form Submission":{"main":[[{"node":"Keep Valid Leads","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Keep Valid Leads":{"main":[[{"node":"Segment Audience","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Segment Audience":{"main":[[{"node":"Step 1 — Welcome (Slack)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Tag for Slow Nurture","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Step 1 — Welcome (Slack)":{"main":[[{"node":"Wait Before Step 2","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Wait Before Step 2":{"main":[[{"node":"Converted Already?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Converted Already?":{"main":[[{"node":"Step 2 — Value Nudge (Slack)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Mark Converted — Stop Drip","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Step 2 — Value Nudge (Slack)":{"main":[[{"node":"Update Drip Status","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Update Drip Status":{"main":[[{"node":"Cap Batch Volume","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cap Batch Volume":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (HubSpot)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (HubSpot)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag for Slow Nurture":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Mark Converted — Stop Drip":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"c5d2b0cc-25dc-4cec-835c-e205c4dd0388","id":"FDX04396"}